---
title: Jamaican Beef Patties with Apple Slaw
description: Our Culinary Team are always thinking of new ways to share the love. This easy hack on our childhood favourite was a big hit in our kitchen. We think that it will be in yours too! We've taken the best of a Jamaican pattie; flavourful mince in a great pastry! Our pre-rolled puff pastry is easy to use with a simple fill, gather, pinch and bake technique. Served with a sweet and crunchy Apple Slaw, we believe we've got you covered!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/jamaican-beef-patties-5a537cb8.jpg
